<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>找不到您请求的页面</title>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, minimum-scale=1.0, user-scalable=no">
  <style>
  html {
    font-size: 10px;
    height: 100%;
  }

  body {
    height: 100%;
    overflow: hidden;
    color: #2E2F30;
    background: #282828 url('data:image/png;base64,');
    font-family: arial, sans-serif;
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 1.4rem;
  }

  .container {
    height: 100%;
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    position: relative;
  }

  .content {
    color: #fff;
    top: 30%;
    left: 10%;
    position: absolute;
    z-index: 3;
  }

  .content__title {
    font-size: 2.6rem;
    color: #ffffff;
  }

  .content__tip {
    font-size: 1.6rem;
    color: #9d9d9d;
    margin: 1.3rem 0 2.7rem;
  }

  .content__link {
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    color: #9d9d9d;
    padding: 1rem 2rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    border-radius: 2px;
    background-color: #414141;
  }

  .content__link:hover {
    color: #f2f2f2;
    background-color: #717171;
  }

  .content__link:last-child {
    margin-left: 3.6rem;
  }

  .animal {
    position: absolute;
    right: 0;
    width: 60%;
    z-index: 3;
    bottom: -9%;
    transition: bottom 1s;
  }

  .animal:hover {
    bottom: 0;
  }

  .mountain-1, .mountain-2 {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 0;
    max-height: 50%;
  }

  .mountain-1,
  .mountain-2 {
    right: 0;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .mountain-1 {
    left: 0;
    z-index: 2;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .content {
      top: 20%;
      left: auto;
      right: 8%;
      z-index: 20;
    }

    .content__title {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }

    .content__tip {
      font-size: 1.4rem;
    }

    .content__link {
    font-size: 1.6rem;
    }

    .content__link:last-child {
      margin-left: 2rem;
    }

    .animal {
      bottom: -4%;
      width: 100%;
      right: -25%;
    }

    .mountain-1 {
      left: -10%;
    }

    .mountain-1, .mountain-2 {
      max-height: 35%;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 320px) {
    .content {
      left: 10%;
      top: 15%;
    }

    .content__links {
      display: block;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .content__link {
      display: inline-block;
      min-width: 100px;
    }

    .content__link:last-child {
      margin-top: 20px;
      margin-left: 0;
    }
  }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <!-- This file lives in public/404.html -->
  <div class="container">
    <div class="content">
      <div class="content__title">抱歉，我们找不到您请求的页面。</div>
      <div class="content__tip">您可以选择掉头返回上一页或者回到网站首页</div>
      <div class="content__links">
        <a class="content__link" href="javascript:;" onclick="javascript:history.back(-1);" alt="返回首页"> 返回上一页</a>
        <a class="content__link" href="/" alt="返回首页"> 返回首页</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <img class="animal" src="data:image/png;base64," />
  </div>
  <div class="mountain-1">
    <img src="data:image/png;base64," />
  </div>

  <div class="mountain-2">
    <img src="data:image/png;base64," />
  </div>
</body>
</html>
